	.string "LITTLEROOT.\p"
	.string "HOENN's unusual right now.\n"
	.string "We'll talk when you arrive.\p"
	.string "Your mom said you just reached town.\p"
	.string "Come by the lab, {PLAYER}.\n"
	.string "I'll be waiting.$(FC 0x01)\p"
	.string "$"

